text: This stretch of the park faces the open sea, gives you a vast and wide feeling of mother nature. Speckled in the distance are fish farms that rear marine fish to serve the palate of our people. Channeling busily in the background are cargo ships that will dock at Pasir Gudang, Johor.
Though not so accessible on public transpo,  the location is better than other BBQ pits in the east area...
